# Pixel Runner V1.1.1
controls: A: kick
          W: launch
          S: slide
      SPACE: jump

## new updates: 
4/17/2014---fixed minor gravity bug, altered point system to accept gold bar bonuses

### Description:

       Pixel Runner is a simple yet addicting game made by up-and coming programmer Kbossthegreat.
It uses JavaScript coding to provide a smooth gameplay, and dynamic controls aid performance. Try to get a great point value before you die, then respawn and try again!
